name: Shivam Plywood Industries Punjab
overview: Established in 1985, we “M.S. Enterprises” is engaged in manufacturing and supplying of Embroidery Cone, Plastic T.F.O., Embroidery & Threading Cone, Plastic Textile Machinery Spare Parts and Embroidery Roll. We have been in the business of manufacturing these products such as Plastic Baby Cone, Baby Cone, Y Cone, V Shaped Cone, Silk Bobbin, Twisting Roll, T.F.O. Roll, Plastic Twisting Roll, Texturising Tube, Plastic T.F.O. Bobbin for over 25 years. Our products are in high demand in the textile industry across the entire country. The textile machinery that we manufacture and supply, find enhanced applications in textile manufacturing where continuous thread spinning and power looms require machinery that is durable. We have been catering to the clients in major textile hubs like Surat, Bangalore, Salem and Ludhiana. Our products have earned a mark of distinction in quality by our clients in these industrial areas. To manufacture high grade components we source our stock of raw materials from trusted suppliers only. This ensures that the quality is consistent across the production cycle and the processing of machines remains fairly consistent.
